quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  21,94,Motero aliyense amene achita ntchito zabwino ndipo ndi wokhulupirira moona ntchito zake sizidzakanidwa ayi. Ndithudi Ife timazilemba zonse m’Buku la chiwerengero
  21,95,Ndipo ndi koletsedwa kuti mudzi umene tidawuwononga kuti ubwererenso
  21,96,Mpaka pamene anthu a Ya-juj ndi Majuj adzamasulidwa ndipo iwo adzakhala akutsika kuchokera kumalo aliwonse wokwera
  21,97,"Ndipo pamene lonjezo loona lidzafika, maso a anthu onse osakhulupirira adzapenyetsetsa mwamantha nati “Tsoka kwa ife! Ndithudi ife tidali osalabadira zimenezi. Zoonadi ife tidali ochita zoipa.”"
  21,98,"Ndithudi! Inu pamodzi ndi zimene mukupembedza kuonjezera pa Mulungu, mudzakhala nkhuni za ku Gahena! Kumeneko nonse mudzalowako"
  21,99,"Iyo ikadakhala milungu, siikadalowa kumeneko ndipo onse adzakhala kumeneko"
  21,100,Kumeneko iwo adzalira ndipo adzakhala osamva
  21,101,"Ndithudi iwo amene tawaonetsera chifundo chathu, iwo adzakhala kutali ndi moto"
  21,102,Iwo sadzamva mkokomo wake pamene iwo ali kumene mitima yawo imafuna mpaka kalekale
  21,103,"Zoopsa sizidzawadandaulitsa ayi ndipo Angelo adzawalandira iwo nati,“Ili ndi tsiku lanu limene inu mudalonjezedwa.”"
  21,104,"Tsiku limene tidzapinde thambo monga momwe timapindira tsamba la Buku. Monga momwe tidayamba chilengedwe choyamba momwemonso tidzachibwezeranso. Ili, ndithudi, ndi lonjezo kwa Ife. Ndithudi, Ife, tidzachita motero"
  21,105,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ife tidalemba m’Buku la Masalimo, motsatira chikumbutso kuti akapolo anga angwiro adzakhala ku dziko lapansi"
  21,106,Ndithudi mu ili muli Uthenga womveka kwa anthu amene amapembedza Mulungu
  21,107,Ndipo sitidakutumize iwe pa chifukwa china koma ngati madalitso kwa zolengedwa zonse
  21,108,"Nena, “Zavumbulutsidwa kwa ine kuti Mulungu wanu ndi mmodzi yekha. Kodi inu mudzadzipereka kwa Iye?”"
  21,109,"Koma ngati iwo safuna kumvera nena, “Ine ndili kukuchenjezani kuti tonse tidziwe. Ine sindidziwa kuti chimene mwalonjezedwa chidza msanga kapena chikadali patali.”"
  21,110,Ndithudi Mulungu amadziwa zonse zimene mumayankhula mokweza ndipo amadziwanso zimene mubisa
  21,111,Ndipo ine sindidziwa ngati awa ndi mayeso kwa inu ndi chisangalalo cha kanthawi kochepa
  21,112,"Iye anati, “Ambuye wanga! Weruzani mwachilungamo! Ambuye wathu ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha amene chithandizo chake chimafunika pa zimene inu muonjezera.”"